{"id": 564, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都如何使用大众点评？", "description": "我对大众点评的感情：虽说我也不怎么信大众点评，但去到一个没有大众点评的城市，我也有点慌。", "record_count": 8206, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2016060616184673ZX4sEMB8jehzCq.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-10T11:00:51Z", "options": [{"id": 17408, "content": "这广告做的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129152}, {"id": 18690, "content": "大众点评是啥？好吃么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258974}, {"id": 16389, "content": "平时搜索到感兴趣的餐馆统统用大众点评收藏起来 然后一家一家拔草 说不定还有优惠团购这些活动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215329}, {"id": 16134, "content": "看来只用它来买电影票的只有我一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132715}, {"id": 16135, "content": "在上头搜搜附近的大保健评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226143}, {"id": 16136, "content": "上次厦门一家黑店我们都坐下了，我看了一眼大众点评，顺利逃脱。不然三只虾可以吃掉500块。", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231348}, {"id": 16138, "content": "写点评的时候标新立异", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211133UbpWfhtzXJO76ykc.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 230879}, {"id": 19214, "content": "这广告打的，我给你满分（没用过大众点评，准去下←_←）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136426}, {"id": 16144, "content": "偶尔用用 陌生餐馆点菜神器", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241510}, {"id": 16663, "content": "以前一般用大众，但后来发现糯米有时团得更便宜一点就用糯米了。但大众的选择范围更多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234048}, {"id": 16409, "content": "一个打开后找不到联系方式的应用，总是无法预订，就是有评论好看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245288}, {"id": 20761, "content": "最近在云南 一直在用 最大的bug是地图不准…口味描述的还行…还是点个赞吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159089}, {"id": 16158, "content": "开始是餐馆指南，后来发现很多不是当地人写的而是游客写的就觉得没什么参考价值了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238729}, {"id": 15647, "content": "到一个不熟悉的地方会打开大众点评看餐馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1674, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 20767, "content": "1、遇到不好的餐馆会重重吐槽\r\n2、遇到不熟悉的城市好好找找\r\n3、遇到聚餐的时候买买买优惠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234658}, {"id": 15648, "content": "我是深度用户，会写几百字点评骂餐馆那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 152, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 15649, "content": "结账的时候会打开点评看看有没有团购", "image": null, "praise_count": 1055, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 16161, "content": "没事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241893}, {"id": 16164, "content": "不是吃货，朋友来我的城市想吃好吃的，就用大众点评找…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241934}, {"id": 18725, "content": "一般出差，和同事一起完全无法决定吃什么的时候。平或者逛到城市的不熟悉的角落。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260615}, {"id": 16167, "content": "用了快10年了吧？原来那么简陋个网站，转眼之间沧海桑田！加油吧！惭愧的我，用了那么久，只留了一次评价，而且还是为了领取一瓶腐乳", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241974}, {"id": 17961, "content": "就是便宜才会用", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211225UnaXNjAVFK92EZHx.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256526}, {"id": 20778, "content": "在国外找餐厅 通过大众点评 进去一看全是天朝人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214539}, {"id": 16685, "content": "用来排除不能吃的餐厅。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248566}, {"id": 16941, "content": "深度体验国际文艺", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211153GmW1uZXY5fbotzlN.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250580}, {"id": 16942, "content": "深度体验国际文艺", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211153AL8uXealF4rqK0ok.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250580}, {"id": 16175, "content": "搜索附近的馆子，仅此而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242069}, {"id": 16177, "content": "不知道吃什么时，以及吃完买单时", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234473}, {"id": 16182, "content": "从来没用过", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208777}, {"id": 16694, "content": "永远不要看那些表扬的评论或者推荐菜，一定要懂得如何看差评和鉴别评论的真伪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248695}, {"id": 16183, "content": "店家有标明大众点评优惠的时候再用", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233391}, {"id": 16184, "content": "不知道吃什么的时候会看看 到一个不熟悉的环境会找找附近有什么好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237140}, {"id": 16187, "content": "想吐槽好久，真的不好用，也被坑过几次，地图带错过几次，但是没有大众点评，去哪心里都好慌。。。尤其是旅游城市", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195783}, {"id": 16192, "content": "大众和美团还有百度糯米一起用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242357}, {"id": 16193, "content": "就没人用闪惠吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201497}, {"id": 16707, "content": "主要当地图用，看看新到的地方哪有好吃的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228349}, {"id": 16197, "content": "还是比较靠谱的，照着上面的美食去吃基本不会很触雷，而且在国外也很好用！！每次在国外用大众都觉得世界都是中国的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242452}, {"id": 16199, "content": "确实好用，国外也能用，看当地景点和美食的点评，去日本自由行就是靠大众点评吃到很多攻略上没有的好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240324}, {"id": 16203, "content": "喜欢看商家跟顾客在评论里撕逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156621}, {"id": 15948, "content": "去到一个陌生城市，大众点评比其他旅游app，更像是我的旅游指南。", "image": null, "praise_count": 657, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238951}, {"id": 16204, "content": "没用过", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227970}, {"id": 15949, "content": "大众点评的死忠粉^_^", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211802XAjq4StkEPQH1V0J.jpg", "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217421}, {"id": 15950, "content": "我属于伸手党，看看，听听", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227387}, {"id": 16209, "content": "多写点评中奖多，吃货越来越快乐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229243}, {"id": 15954, "content": "我是钻石用户，会写上千字的点评，但我也并不相信所谓五星餐厅，一般我会选择看好友点评，因为我的好友一般也是大v", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237496}, {"id": 15955, "content": "大众点评就是传说中的\"本地人\"啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 378, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236357}, {"id": 15957, "content": "女朋友问今天去哪儿的时候…", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232086}, {"id": 15958, "content": "大众点评就当美团用的", "image": null, "praise_count": 183, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209723}, {"id": 16214, "content": "不大使用了 以前看榜单 现在高质量用户少了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242747}, {"id": 16215, "content": "无团购不开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242227}]}